Package: dgxtop
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: DGXTOP Ubuntu Team <noreply@example.com>
Installed-Size: 120
Depends: python3-psutil, python3-rich, python3:any
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Description: System monitor for NVIDIA DGX Spark
 A performance monitoring CLI tool for Ubuntu on NVIDIA DGX Spark,
 inspired by asitop for Mac. Provides real-time monitoring of CPU,
 GPU, memory, disk I/O, and network statistics with an interactive
 terminal interface.
